name: Central Vista Rooftop
description: A stylish rooftop venue located in the heart of downtown, offering panoramic city views. The space is perfect for an upscale dining experience. Located on Central Avenue, near major commercial hubs, with a rent fee of $10,000 per month.

name: Bay Park Gardens
description: A serene garden setting in the Bay Park district, ideal for a family-friendly restaurant. This spot is surrounded by greenery and provides a peaceful escape from the city. It’s located near the waterfront, with a rent fee of $7,500 per month.

name: Sunset Corner Lounge
description: A cozy corner space in a trendy neighborhood, perfect for a casual dining restaurant. It’s located on Sunset Boulevard, surrounded by boutiques and cafes, making it a hotspot for foot traffic. The rent fee is $6,000 per month.
